# Once done this will define
#
#  WCECOMPAT_FOUND - system has Wcecompat
#  WCECOMPAT_INCLUDE_DIR - Wcecompat include directory
#  WCECOMPAT_LIBRARIES - Libraries needed to use Wcecompat
